name: Flower Style TI
description:
Genral Info

Flower style was my first ever embedding and still is useable on newer models. It adds alot of flowers to the general image. For best use, I would use it with any kind of portrait type image.

Added Example Images with simple prompt from:

  • Kenshi

  • AbyssOrangeMix_nsfw

Usage

To use this embedding you have to download the file aswell as drop it into the "\stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings" folder

To use it in a prompt: "flower_style"

For some models it can be to strong, so use this instead

"(flower_style:0.8)"

Have fun :)
